item.title: About Naughty Monsta
item.description: Scientists have spent huge amount of time & effort on discovering different animal species, they've travelled the world to hunt down the animals that have never been seen & heard before, and tell us about these new discoveries. But there are some creatures - “monstas” - they've been hiding from us all the time in their universe, which is a universe compleletely separated from the 3-dimentional universe that we humans live in.
